summary: With over 12 years of experience designing for significant Irish, British, Canadian and Indian companies, I have a passion for creating exceptional user experiences that delight and engage users. My expertise lies in product design, design systems, user research, prototyping and design strategy. I am skilled at collaborating with cross-functional teams to drive projects from ideation to launch. My design approach is user-centered and data-driven, always with a focus on creating designs that meet both user needs and business KPIs.
